        "meta_description": "Jesse Tyler Ferguson said his role on 'Modern Family' caused the public to be more accepting of the fact that he was gay. On this week's episode of his 'Dinner's on Me' podcast, he explained that people were more welcoming to him because he was famous, and he felt like that became his \"superpower.\"",
